parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure and Rod Bearing Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine and rod bearings can cause the vehicle to stall or lose motive power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine makes a knocking or tapping noise
the vehicle loses power
the check engine light illuminates
the oil light illuminates
smoke comes from the engine compartment
the vehicle stalls or fails to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine knocking or tapping noise can be a precursor to engine failure, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine makes a knocking or tapping noise
the vehicle vibrates
the engine light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to repair or recall vehicles with defective engines can lead to accidents or leave drivers stranded.
symptoms: The dealer or manufacturer refuses to repair or replace the engine
the vehicle is not included in the recall
the repair is not covered under warranty.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Pedal Sticking and Failure to Return
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sticking brake pedal can cause accidents, loss of control, and failure to stop, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal sticks to the floor
brake pedal does not return to its normal position
brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
brake lights remain on
grinding noises
vibration
and difficulty driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause fires, damage to the vehicle's electrical components, and leave the driver stranded, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle catches fire
smoke is detected
burning odor is present
electrical wires are damaged

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear light assembly can cause the brake lights to malfunction, leading to accidents or injuries, and can also cause fires due to overheating.
symptoms: Rear lights blow out frequently
brake lights do not function

sockets are melted
and lights are extremely hot to the touch.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, make it difficult to shift gears, and lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle stalls
and the gear shift does not engage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine and cooling system can cause the vehicle to stall, overheat, and lead to accidents or injuries.
